# supermart_grocery_sales
Supermart Grocery Sales Analysis

This project analyzes grocery sales data from a supermart to understand sales performance, customer behavior, and product demand. The dataset includes details such as order date, category, sub-category, region, sales, profit, discount, and quantity sold.

Along with data analysis and visualization, machine learning models are applied to predict sales and identify patterns that support better business decision-making.

